{"tid":623781,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"絕地求生pubg約戰TG&whatsapp群（電腦版）","createTime":"2018-04-10T09:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T09:23:33.000Z","uid":130889,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"14a7d9b0e29318d44c9ba07f4f66862a5ad522f3","tid":623781,"uid":130889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T09:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTG群&amp;whatsapp 入面可以搵隊<br />\n歡迎加入"},{"pid":"6c1ad20ac6c36cd7972c1e56bcc21342f8691e65","tid":623781,"uid":130889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T03:24:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e14fc5bbdf5353a349b646b70c711c9ab5928a6","tid":623781,"uid":130889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31bf4e0e3cfadc8f61fe5a891ba777c748f0d174","tid":623781,"uid":130889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb0a0ac2896c761bd9021ac03796f15f6179734","tid":623781,"uid":130889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:11:14.000Z","msg":"[PUBG_TW] 限時活動模式 &ndash; War mode<br />\n<br />\n親愛的PUBG玩家們，大家好！<br />\n <br />\n和大家分享一個好消息，介紹一下這週開放的全新限時活動模式！<br />\n <br />\n大家來見識一下吧~<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OwvKFOfckeM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOwvKFOfckeM&d=5v%2FDwfTm9hZZ%2BvngnM%2Ffv%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=8d981c39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OwvKFOfckeM</a><br />\n<br />\nWar Mode為死鬥類型的遊戲模式，於小地區持續進行團體戰為此模式的特色。<br />\n開始即可擁有主武器，進行快速又激烈的戰鬥。死亡後也可以復活並維持進行戰鬥！<br />\n <br />\n●活動模式時間: 4/13(五) 10:00 ~ 4/16(一) 10:00<br />\n <br />\n●活動模式配對方式<br />\n1. 活動模式的配對方式為如下。<br />\n - NA/ EU/ AS/ SEA/ OC: TPP &amp; FPP<br />\n - KR/ JP/ SA: TPP<br />\n2. 透過邀請好友功能，最多可組成10人隊伍並利用隨機(Auto Matching)的方式進行配對。<br />\n <br />\n●活動模式主要項目<br />\n1. 限於Erangel地圖進行，天氣為晴天。<br />\n2. 伍人數為10位，3隊進行遊戲(最多共30位)。但依照配對情況部分隊伍的人數可能未達10位。<br />\n3. 進入遊戲的時刻，就會顯示可進行遊戲的安全地區(白區)限制。由復活飛機固定時間内復活。<br />\n4. 復活時具有AR或DMR其中一把主武器及隨機的一把手槍。並獲得一等背心、頭盔、手榴彈各一個。<br />\n5. 每90秒會有補給機，補給箱的内容與一般遊戲相同。在地圖上也可獲得武器和防具等道具。<br />\n6. War mode上不會開啓紅區與觀戰模式。<br />\n <br />\n●活動模式規矩<br />\n1. 首先到達目標分數(200分)時遊戲結束，獲得分數的方式如下。<br />\n -Kill: +3分<br />\n -DBNO: +1分<br />\n -Revive: +1分<br />\n -Team Kill 或 Team DBNO: -5分<br />\n2. 若限制時間(15分鐘)内未達目標分數, 分數最高隊伍將獲勝。<br />\n <br />\n若想瞭解進一步的活動詳細内容, 請至FAQ確認。<br />\n喜歡刺激戰鬥的玩家們請多參與並向我方提供反饋！ <br />\n<br />\n感謝"},{"pid":"845eacfd8c3f50cb79986593d277b7492cd7be18","tid":623781,"uid":156520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:53:46.000Z","msg":"新手已加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da9fd329aab76b545b9d72db3973eaba2cea997","tid":623781,"uid":130889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8a683a93a496b1e56c9a9c21be91d7e1ecfdfe","tid":623781,"uid":130889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c178d555b470bb61e4d6567a400925d0950dd481","tid":623781,"uid":130889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ecae8478887d417a24704939bcb911676e5afe","tid":623781,"uid":130889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim